# SANER Measure Consumer Actor Requirements
@SANER @SANER-MeasureConsumer

Feature: MeasureConsumer-1 The Measure Consumer shall implement either the Pull Option or the Push Option.Feature: MeasureConsumer-2 A Measure Consumer that implements the Pull Option shall conform to the
[Measure Consumer Pull Capability Statement](CapabilityStatement-MeasureConsumerPull.html).Feature: MeasureConsumer-3 A Measure Consumer that implements the Push Option shall provide a CapabilityStatement when queried via [base]/metadata.Feature: MeasureConsumer-4 A Measure Consumer that implements the Push Option shall conform to the
[Measure Consumer Push Capability Statement](CapabilityStatement-MeasureConsumerPull.html).